</code></pre> <p>工具代码：</p> C++<pre><code>AcGePoint3d TransformPoint(const AcGePoint3d &amp;point, int nFromType, int nToType)
{
    AcGePoint3d pt;
    //从ucs转到wcs
    struct resbuf rbFrom, rbTo;
    rbFrom.restype = RTSHORT;
    rbFrom.resval.rint = nFromType; // from wcs
